      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 66,
      "message": "I don't think this is the right thing to do. A filter runs in a multi-threaded environment and may be shared among requests. In this case multiple threads calling doFilter() will override each other's permissionsServices. The old code was thread-safe because permissionsServices was initiated only once on the creation of a filter instance.",
